ABB, Schneider Electric Bidding for Beijing Leader: Reuter Link

-- B y   C h r i s   P e t e r s o n
-- 
2011-06-06T03:52:34Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-06/abb-schneider-electric-bidding-for-beijing-leader-reuter-link.html
ABB Ltd. (ABBN)  and  Schneider Electric SA (SU) 
are part of a second round of bidding for Beijing Leader &
Harvest Technologies Co, which is owned by private equity firms
Affinity Equity Partners and Unitas Capital, Reuters reported,
citing people familiar with the matter.  Beijing Leader, which makes energy saving equipment for
heavy machinery, may fetch as much as $700 million, the news
service said.   Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
